---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import RelatedPosts from "../components/RelatedPosts.astro";

const metaTitle = "Wheelchair Accessible Car Modification";
const metaDescription = "Guide to ramps, lifts, platforms, and hand controls to make cars wheelchair accessible.";
const currentSlug = "wheelchair-accessible-car-modification";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith("/") ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
const ogImage = `${base}logo.png`;
---

<BaseLayout title={metaTitle} description={metaDescription} headerVariant="solid">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta property="og:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={ogImage} />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content={ogImage} />
  </Fragment>

  <article class="article">
    <header class="article-head">
      <p class="article-date">June 19, 2023 Â· by vivek</p>
      <h1>Wheelchair Accessible Car Modification</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="article-grid">
      <div class="article-body">
        <p>
          If you or a loved one uses a wheelchair, you may be wondering how to make it easier to get around. One option is
          to modify your car so that it is wheelchair accessible. There are a number of different modifications that can be
          made, and the best option for you will depend on your individual needs.
        </p>

        <h2>Types of Modifications</h2>
        <p>Some of the most common wheelchair accessible car modifications include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Ramps: A ramp can be installed in the back of your car to allow a wheelchair user to easily get in and out.</li>
          <li>Lifts: A lift can be installed in the floor of your car to raise and lower a wheelchair user into the car.</li>
          <li>Platforms: A platform can be installed in the back of your car to provide a level surface for a wheelchair user to sit on.</li>
          <li>Hand controls: Hand controls can be installed in your car to allow a wheelchair user to drive.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Cost of Modifications</h2>
        <p>
          The cost of wheelchair accessible car modifications can vary depending on the type of modification and the make
          and model of your car. In general, ramps and lifts are the most expensive modifications, while platforms and hand
          controls are less expensive.
        </p>

        <h2>Finding a Qualified Modifier</h2>
        <p>
          If you are considering having your car modified, it is important to find a qualified modifier. A qualified
          modifier will have experience working with wheelchair accessible car modifications and will be able to recommend
          the best modification for your needs.
        </p>

        <h2>Conclusion</h2>
        <p>
          Wheelchair accessible car modifications can make it easier for people with disabilities to get around. If you or
          a loved one uses a wheelchair, consider having your car modified to make it more accessible.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="sidebar" aria-label="Products">
        <div class="products-card">
          <h2>Products</h2>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus-accelerate" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-bSUnSfkD-8"
                title="TurnPlus Accelerate video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus Accelerate</p>
              <p class="product-link">trueassistech.com/products/turnplus-accelerate</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/ramplus-for-maruti-suzuki-eeco" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Xu3K_KgzS5Y"
                title="RamPlus for Maruti Suzuki Eeco video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">RamPlus for Maruti Suzuki Eeco</p>
              <p class="product-link">trueassistech.com/products/ramplus-for-maruti-suzuki-eeco</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/hydraulic-wheelchair-lift" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ad_M9zIw668"
                title="Hydraulic wheelchair lift video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">Hydraulic wheelchair lift</p>
              <p class="product-link">trueassistech.com/products/hydraulic-wheelchair-lift</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </article>

  <RelatedPosts currentSlug={currentSlug} />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .article {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .article-head h1 {
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .article-date {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .article-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .article-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #451e5d;
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0.15rem;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-body);
  }

  .sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }

  .products-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 0.9rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .products-card h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.6rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    background: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .product-card:hover {
    border-color: #451e5d;
  }

  .video-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #000;
  }

  .video-frame iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  .product-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }

  .product-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-link {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .article-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
